  "instructions": [
    "Press the tofu for 20 minutes and crumble it into a bowl.",
    "Heat olive oil in a skillet over medium heat and add the crumbled tofu.",
    "Stir in smoked paprika, garlic, and ginger, cooking until tofu is lightly browned.",
    "Deglaze with soy sauce and lemon juice, then toss in chopped cilantro and scallions.",
    "Remove tofu from the skillet and let it cool slightly.",
    "Lay softened pandan leaf wraps flat on a clean surface and divide tofu mixture evenly among them.",
    "Top each wrap with a spoonful of gherkin relish.",
    "Sprinkle toasted sesame seeds over the relish.",
    "Fold the sides of each wrap over the filling and roll tightly.",
    "Serve immediately or wrap in parchment for a snack later."
  ],
